OL,7,FA council leader who refused to
OL,8,Fapologise to the victims of a
OL,9,Fpaedophile head teacher has resigned.
OL,11,FPlaid Cymru councillor Dyfrig Siencyn
OL,12,Ffaced criticism after failing to
OL,13,Fapologise to the victims of Neil
OL,14,FFoden, who was jailed for 17 years
OL,15,Fthis year after being found guilty of
OL,16,Fsexually abusing four girls over a
OL,17,Ffour-year period.
