OL,7,FCllr Siencyn, who led Cyngor Gwynedd
OL,8,Ffor seven years, had last week refused
OL,9,Fto apologise to victims on behalf of
OL,10,Fthe council or back calls for a public
OL,11,Finquiry in an interview with Newyddion
OL,12,FS4C, which sparked controversy and led
OL,13,Fto him rowing back on his original
OL,14,Fcomments.
OL,16,FIn the S4C interview, he said: "We
OL,17,Fneed to deal with this early and
OL,18,Fquickly, and I think the Child
OL,19,FPractice Review is the best way to do
OL,20,Fthis.
