OL,7,FCllr Siencyn has now stood down as
OL,8,Fleader of the Plaid Cymru group at the
OL,9,Fcouncil and the local authority's
OL,10,Fleader.
OL,12,FFoden was found guilty of 19 charges,
OL,13,Fincluding 12 of sexual activity with a
OL,14,Fchild, at a trial which ended in May.
