OL,5,Cresigns
OL,7,FCouncillor Siencyn notified the
OL,8,Fcouncil's chair on Thursday, 17
OL,9,FOctober, of his decision to step down
OL,10,Fas council leader, saying in a
OL,11,Fstatement that he is "deeply sorry for
OL,12,Fthe pain" that Foden's victims and
OL,13,Ftheir families have gone through.
OL,15,FThe local authority is conducting a
OL,16,FChild Practice Review to try and
OL,17,Festablish what lessons can be learnt.
