OL,7,F"I must acknowledge that this most
OL,8,Frecent period ` and the horrific
OL,9,Finformation which has come to light
OL,10,Fabout the unforgivable crimes of the
OL,11,Fpaedophile Neil Foden ` has been the
OL,12,Fmost challenging for the Council as an
OL,13,Fauthority and for myself as Leader.
OL,15,F"I am deeply sorry for the pain the
OL,16,Fvictims and their families have gone
OL,17,Fthrough at the hands of this man, and
OL,18,Fthey remain at the forefront of my
OL,19,Fmind."
